SUMMARY:Weird Dreams Dance Party/Book Release
DESCRIPTION:Local artist HG just finished a hilarious new comic book with over 200 BIZARRE dreams inside! To celebrate\, we’re having a PAJAMA DANCE PARTY!\n\nCome to Delta of Venus\, 4/10 from 5-9 (aka 2nd Friday Art About) to:\n-buy a 1st edition copy of the new book.\n-see a brand new\, dream-based art exhibition.\n-DANCE!\n*Dress Code: pajamas\, wacky or wacky pajamas.
