SUMMARY:Live Music & Food Truck
DESCRIPTION:🍷🎶 Live Music & Food Truck Night at Great Bear Vineyards 🎶🍽️\nFriday\, April 10 | 5–8pm\nTicket Includes: Glass of Wine & Live Music\nEase into the weekend with a laid-back Friday evening at the vineyard—great wine\, live music\, and bold\, flavorful food all in one beautiful setting. ✨\n🎸 Odd Man Out returns to Great Bear! A true Yolo County favorite for over 20 years\, they’ll be bringing their signature mix of ‘60s & ‘70s classics (plus a few originals!) with a rich\, full sound featuring guitars\, mandolin\, keys\, harmonica\, bass\, and drums. Catch their live set from 6–7:30pm.\n🍤 Soul Ona Roll will be onsite from 5–8pm\, serving up their crave-worthy Cajun & Creole-inspired dishes—including fan-favorite Voodoo fries. Come hungry and support this fantastic local food truck (no outside food\, please!).\nYour ticket includes a glass of wine\, with more available by the glass or bottle as you relax\, sip\, and soak in the vineyard views.\n✨ Food Truck: 5–8pm\n🎶 Live Music: 6–7:30pm\nGreat music\, delicious food\, and a welcoming vineyard vibe—the perfect way to start your weekend. We can’t wait to see you there!
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/live-music-food-truck/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards (Great Bear)\, 24800 County Rd 101A
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink,Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Odd-Man-Out-Thumbnail.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
GEO:38.5818013;-121.7499687
