SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout Reception: David Kalb and Nancy Gelbard
DESCRIPTION:A collaborative exhibition by David Kalb and Nancy Gelbard\, exploring how two artists respond to the same moments in distinct yet connected ways. David’s street photographs capture spontaneous\, unguarded scenes from everyday life while Nancy’s oil paintings are created directly from these photographs\, allowing her to revisit and reinterpret the images. \nMoving from lens to brush\, the work reflects an ongoing dialogue between two ways of seeing—and the shared experience of observing the world together. In addition to their shared artistic experience\, each artist is also exhibiting individual pieces of their work.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/2nd-friday-artabout-reception-david-kalb-and-nancy-gelbard/
LOCATION:The Paint Chip\, 217 F Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art
