SUMMARY:Round Robin w/ Rita Hosking\, Richard March\, & Jim Bruno Live
DESCRIPTION:An intimate evening of storytelling\, harmony\, and California grown songwriting. Three acclaimed Sacramento area artists share the stage in a round robin format-trading songs\, swapping stories\, and weaving their voices together in a uniquely collaborative performance. No setlists\, no barriers-just honest songs\, lived experience\, and the magic that happens when great writers listen to one another. \nRita Hosking – A celebrated voice in California folk and Americana\, Rita Hosking is known for her soaring vocals\, vivid storytelling\, and deep connection to the rural West. Her award winning songwriting blends folk\, country\, and mountain soul\, earning praise from international roots publications and audiences across the U.S. and Europe. Hosking’s performances are raw\, resonant\, and rooted in place. \nRichard March – Sacramento songwriter Richard March brings a warm\, narrative driven style shaped by Americana\, folk rock\, and the lyrical traditions of the West Coast. His songs carry emotional clarity and melodic ease\, delivered with a seasoned performer’s touch. March’s work has earned regional acclaim for its sincerity\, craftsmanship\, and timeless feel. \nJim Bruno – A veteran songwriter and educator\, Jim Bruno has penned songs recorded by major artists and featured in film and television. His writing is marked by emotional precision\, melodic strength\, and a deep understanding of the craft. Bruno’s performances balance heart\, humor\, and hard won wisdom\, making him a standout presence in any songwriter circle. \nFormat & Experience:\nThree artists seated in a shared circle\nEach takes turns performing one song at a time\nOrganic conversation\, harmonies\, and spontaneous collaboration\nA listening room atmosphere that highlights lyrics\, stories\, and craft\nPerfect for audiences who appreciate songwriting at its most personal and unfiltered. \nPresented by Left of the Dial and KDRT \n 
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/round-robin-w-rita-hosking-richard-march-jim-bruno-live/
LOCATION:Melon Ball – Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd\, Suite #1\, Davis\, California\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/RoundRobin.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Watermelon Music":MAILTO:watermelonmusicdavis@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR